content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1260.22 - Pedestrian travel restricted

State Regulations

No person shall travel on any portion of an air
terminal except upon the roads, walks or places provided for the particular
class of traffic; nor occupy the road or walks in such manner as to hinder or
obstruct their proper use. Notes
